# Generated by Cargo
# will have compiled files and executables
debug
target

# These are backup files generated by rustfmt
**/*.rs.bk

# MSVC Windows builds of rustc generate these, which store debugging information
*.pdb

# Generated by cargo mutants
# Contains mutation testing data
**/mutants.out*/

# RustRover
#  JetBrains specific template is maintained in a separate JetBrains.gitignore that can
#  be found at https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Global/JetBrains.gitignore
#  and can be added to the global gitignore or merged into this file.  For a more nuclear
#  option (not recommended) you can uncomment the following to ignore the entire idea folder.
#.idea/

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Claude Code — open-source policy: the SHARED agent team is committed so anyone
# who clones the repo (and CI) gets it. Only personal/local/transient files are
# ignored. TRACKED on purpose: .claude/agents, .claude/skills, .claude/hooks,
# .claude/briefs, .claude/settings.json, and every CLAUDE.md.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/**/*.local.json
.claude/**/*.local.*
.claude/logs/
.claude/cache/
.claude/.cache/
.claude/scratch/
.claude/tmp/

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Secrets & sensitive files — NEVER commit
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.local.env
secrets.*
*.secret
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
*.crt
credentials.json
*.credentials
.netrc

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CodeCache local index — regenerable & can be large; keep config, drop the DB
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.codecache/*.db
.codecache/*.db-shm
.codecache/*.db-wal
.codecache/cache/
# (.codecache/config.toml is intentionally tracked)

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OS / editor noise
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*~
.vscode/
